code/paper/main.out
# NOTE: numbers.tex, tables/*.tex, and figures/*.pdf are auto-generated
# but the current MOCK versions are committed so the paper compiles
# out-of-the-box for reviewers. `make tex` / `make figures` overwrite
# them with real-run values.

